channel.title: Frisco Real Estate Video Blog with Amy and Kevin Smits
channel.description: Our mission at The Smits Team is to be your best resource for Frisco real estate advice. Whether you are a buyer, seller, or investor, our team of professionals can answer any questions you might have about real estate. If you are looking to buy or sell a home, you can get all the information and the latest updates, tips, and tricks from The The Smits Team, your professional Frisco Real Estate Agents.
